{"tid":162032,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"藤原龍也才第 3！日本票選「真的有演技」時下男演員 Top 10 冠軍原來是...","createTime":"2017-03-19T03:28:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T14:51:39.000Z","uid":9573,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c33459e711fecc3ad00dc993ee551883bb3b3fe","tid":162032,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:28:41.000Z","msg":"現在日本戲劇、電影圈最火紅的兩大「漫改王子」山崎賢人和福士蒼汰，時常被日本網友嘲諷「演技太爛」、「演什麼角色看起來都是同一個人」，那麼日本觀眾心目中真的有演技可以期待的時下當紅男演員當中，又會是哪一些男星呢？日本網站《Joshi-Spa》近期就公佈了這項投票結果，意外發現第一名居然讓大家都很信服？<br />\n<br />\n第 10 名、小栗旬。<br />\n<br />\n作為日本當今最知名的帥哥演員，小栗旬已經給人一種大物演員的氣場，不過也有一些日本網友在觀看這個排行榜時吐槽：「小栗旬的演技才沒有外界評價那樣厲害。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63307/58c4d875cb7a4.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63307%2F58c4d875cb7a4.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=4a6d5e13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第 9 名、森山未來。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63307/58c4d87779220.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63307%2F58c4d87779220.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=51227b8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第 8 名、菅田將暉。<br />\n<br />\n個人特色鮮明的菅田將暉，觀眾對於他的演出反應特別呈現兩極化，許多粉絲特別喜歡他毫不做作、無所畏懼的演戲方式，但菅田將暉的穿衣時尚和「濃臉」也時常被一些觀眾嫌棄。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63307/58c4d87868ea5.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63307%2F58c4d87868ea5.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=7e60de6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第 7 名、神木隆之介。<br />\n<br />\n從小就是超火紅童星的神木弟弟，能夠在長大成人之後依然維持這個高的國民好感度，果然還是只有神木才做得到。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63307/58c4d87b8eda9.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63307%2F58c4d87b8eda9.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=18783183&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n並列第 6 名、高橋一生。<br />\n<br />\n《民王》中人氣完全不輸給主角的超搶眼大臣秘書，高橋一生現在長期都是在日劇中扮演配角，卻時常能夠將角色魅力發揮到最大，成為該劇當中數一數二亮眼的人物。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63307/58c4d879c2423.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63307%2F58c4d879c2423.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=a1fcfed5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第 5 名、濱田岳。<br />\n<br />\n北川景子的新版《HERO 2》中，相信大家對於這位娃娃臉檢察官都印象深刻，事實上他也是日本相當知名的實力派演員，年輕時代也曾是《金八老師》學生的一員。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63307/58c4d87c63d08.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63307%2F58c4d87c63d08.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=47ecb167&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第 4 名、岡田准一。<br />\n<br />\n除了木村拓哉之外，當今傑尼斯的演技一哥就非屬岡田淮一莫屬，擁有日本全國公認帥臉的他現在專心在電影圈發展。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63307/58bb94f599a14.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63307%2F58bb94f599a14.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=62869089&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X4UT8J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX4UT8J.png&h=c622a118&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第 3 名、藤原龍也。<br />\n<br />\n在演完夜神月之後，騰原龍也開始踏上揣摩各種悲情角色的演員之路，他同時也是日本觀眾心目中「最適合演崩潰戲份」的男星，畢竟他咆哮那一幕已成經典。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63307/58bb94f34655c.jpeg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63307%2F58bb94f34655c.jpeg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=564d43fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n並列第 3 名、妻夫木聰。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63307/58bb94f497638.jpeg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63307%2F58bb94f497638.jpeg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=0c9698ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第 2  名、松山研一。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63307/58c4d87db4935.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63307%2F58c4d87db4935.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=98930660&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第 1 名、山田孝之。<br />\n<br />\n冠軍就是百變男山田孝之！在看《在世界的中心呼喊愛情》時，你絕對想不到這位美少年，日後居然會成為各種搞怪的「熊樣大叔」，山田孝之的演技普遍受到日本觀眾，同時也有網友提名鈴木亮平、草彅剛及柳樂優彌。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63307/58bb94f3da7b1.jpeg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63307%2F58bb94f3da7b1.jpeg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=fef87a85&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75c50bec6a5395a193e1cf67e60f7035324c2603","tid":162032,"uid":4326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:32:25.000Z","msg":"入黎就係睇朱千雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548188f74f59c9354955a2739e4a835c5a7ac3e9","tid":162032,"uid":11664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:12:29.000Z","msg":"之前好似話藤原龍也係咩天才舞台劇演員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69ceb3dfb9b4797ef168fb185accf9016afb132f","tid":162032,"uid":89507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:19:05.000Z","msg":"山田真係無得輸"},{"pid":"eb6b9e3fc1b4191acec10ccfaacaf9947b020c03","tid":162032,"uid":44975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:25:25.000Z","msg":"都估到係佢<br />\n睇佢做勇者同熱血高校個分別就知"},{"pid":"c42b7de29929155e27df0176412782b84a88feee","tid":162032,"uid":51594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:27:37.000Z","msg":"仲諗住點解碌咗咁耐都冇山田，點知原來係第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但個調查係咪只限40歲以下男星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74c7517a989c6f0802aafd0af32d1f8571b007a0","tid":162032,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:27:58.000Z","msg":"山田實至名歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />在世界中心呼喚愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />白夜行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勇者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"100341a0e665b6ede60ec0f682235b50b07efc77","tid":162032,"uid":66926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:42:06.000Z","msg":"朱千雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82a9a094be51bda3d61f3f776f0bfdf20a92fa25","tid":162032,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T05:08:57.000Z","msg":"第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb72ba007f7a08311d29ed807659799496d86e19","tid":162032,"uid":1713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T05:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://up.gc-img.net/post_img/2014/11/hJjyAUrsmqdW15e_gwey5_32.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fup.gc-img.net%2Fpost_img%2F2014%2F11%2FhJjyAUrsmqdW15e_gwey5_32.jpeg&h=d7a78fb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個大叔先好戲"},{"pid":"89ab8977c482ab7074300cb526ea0d231c3c58d1","tid":162032,"uid":86339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T05:23:10.000Z","msg":"柳樂優彌應該要榜上有名，話曬都係康城影帝"},{"pid":"f6a20f0f78480278e7e072fd6a4b38c307d77056","tid