2032,"uid":39630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T06:27:19.000Z","msg":"山田<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前睇過一集堂本兄弟 山田做嘉賓<br />\n佢話佢好鍾意喺屋企模仿廣告啲對白 仲會演唔多風格同版本出嚟 我心諗佢係咪咁樣練啲演技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de3dd2587b0082169d1c6db6d862b5b613e9cbf5","tid":162032,"uid":39630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T06:28:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>山田<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前睇過一集堂本兄弟 山田做嘉賓<br />\n佢話佢好鍾意喺屋企模仿廣告啲對白 仲會演唔<span style=\"color: red;\">同</span>風格出嚟 我心諗佢係咪咁樣練啲演技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"455fdbda663a68bf54a5e69405eb3058bf8e4fd4","tid":162032,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T06:37:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>山田<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前睇過一集堂本兄弟 山田做嘉賓<br />\n佢話佢好鍾意喺屋企模仿廣告啲對白 仲會演唔多風格同版本出嚟 我心諗佢係咪咁樣練啲演技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個洗頭水廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e0c7688afdebdc65a10f4848fbf69e888853845","tid":162032,"uid":9942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T06:42:55.000Z","msg":"山田拍ps4 啲廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5954674d9748f252a6ceacbaa2bf8092f6dcd7b","tid":162032,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T06:49:23.000Z","msg":"染谷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c507480d9ea8ccb69a39bb132b13da715257efca","tid":162032,"uid":39,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T06:50:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>夜神月叫好戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一直覺得佢做戲好似屙屎唔出咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雖然到目前為止藤原龍也在海外最出名的作品是電影《大逃殺》（Battle Royale） 和 《死亡筆記》（Death Note），但在日本舞台才是他的標誌。日本戲劇史上最年輕的舞台最高賞得主，20歲出頭就橫掃了日本演劇界的所有大獎。同樣是舞台起家的真田廣之和渡邊謙也是到了30多歲才達到他這個高度。藤原代表日本在歐美公演三島由紀夫的近代能樂時，無論是歐洲還是百老匯的評論家，都對他給予世界級演技的贊賞<br />\n<br />\n去到連登竟然變成做戲係屙屎唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fcdd36c00e569bd86ffd6632a7c274238d4c6a6","tid":162032,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T06:57:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>夜神月叫好戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一直覺得佢做戲好似屙屎唔出咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雖然到目前為止藤原龍也在海外最出名的作品是電影《大逃殺》（Battle Royale） 和 《死亡筆記》（Death Note），但在日本舞台才是他的標誌。日本戲劇史上最年輕的舞台最高賞得主，20歲出頭就橫掃了日本演劇界的所有大獎。同樣是舞台起家的真田廣之和渡邊謙也是到了30多歲才達到他這個高度。藤原代表日本在歐美公演三島由紀夫的近代能樂時，無論是歐洲還是百老匯的評論家，都對他給予世界級演技的贊賞<br />\n<br />\n去到連登竟然變成做戲係屙屎唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連登＞所有權威"},{"pid":"3571aef62901d4664db89164bff301804b31c058","tid":162032,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T06:57:47.000Z","msg":"山田真係好正<br />\n佢做戲又夠放個下好嘢<br />\n冇壓力嘅束縛，好靈活自如咁去做戲"},{"pid":"3a572dc4666de80510a1b7268f05b0816f60e718","tid":162032,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T06:59:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>夜神月叫好戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一直覺得佢做戲好似屙屎唔出咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雖然到目前為止藤原龍也在海外最出名的作品是電影《大逃殺》（Battle Royale） 和 《死亡筆記》（Deat